title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Double Rewards on A Superyacht Life
content:
Seek adventure on the high seas and plunder Double Rewards all this week. Salvage sunken cargo, capsize enemy vessels, and fight off amphibious assaults in A Superyacht Life Contact Missions, paying out 2X GTA$ and RP through May 28. Plus, complete three A Superyacht Life Missions to fulfill the Weekly Challenge and claim GTA$100,000.

Visit Captain Darcy on the bridge of your Galaxy Super Yacht (40% off this week) to get started.
